Porter Hall https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Porter_Hall 0 Clifford Porter Hall (September 19, 1888 – October 6, 1953) was an American character actor known for appearing in a number of films in the 1930s and 1940s. Hall played movie villains or comedic incompetent characters.
